{"tid":1630414,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際戰線嚴峻！ＳＯＳ！】面對假新聞／惡意抹黑　請學當撈侵：「ＦＡＫＥ　ＮＥＷＳ！」","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:40:42.000Z","uid":14328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a20d6af8d5daf3e1d6ee303529e10b0ff7c81c56","tid":1630414,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:13.000Z","msg":"有上Twitter既手足應該知<br />\n自從林鄭出左緊急法之後<br />\n國際戰線嘅五毛數量係多左十倍以上<br />\n<br />\n外國人好多時唔知咩事<br />\n正如今日：<br />\n「的士司機發動恐怖襲擊，高速衝撞人群意圖謀殺。」<br />\n<br />\n被五毛講成：<br />\n「無辜的士司機被蒙面暴徒暴打至大量出血，情況危殆。」<br />\n<br />\n有啲鬼佬會信，仲話香港示威者好暴力，變哂質，雖然現階段支持香港示威者既人仲係佔較多數，但係國際戰線再唔打就真係會輸！<br />\n<br />\n希望勇武能夠自衛抗暴嘅時候，和理非能夠幫手上Twitter<br />\nTwitter戰線2000人都唔知有無，嚴重缺人！<br />\n<br />\n面對假新聞／惡意抹黑，幫幫手立即指出佢係FAKE NEWS<br />\n<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/l0Iyau7QcKtKUYIda/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0Iyau7QcKtKUYIda%2Fsource.gif&h=2410fe0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求下大家幫幫手，呢個關鍵時刻，唔可以比政府喺國際戰線上翻盤，將香港示威者描述成失控暴徒！一定要保住美國國會，通過人權與民主法案，如果過唔到，香港人真係會一鋪清袋</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5859b588abcdf93ab886071566dda64ee19eeb9a","tid":1630414,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"邊個大大聲話集中<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間<br />\n<br />\n集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64f54f086885b5cebe5b369787c5a263402f44ae","tid":1630414,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:26:20.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f3dd610131275091a303e4e29adeb6f7d5f3c91","tid":1630414,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/7b26fa4e4ed0f152c81fe8c2f3345abe/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F7b26fa4e4ed0f152c81fe8c2f3345abe%2Ftenor.gif&h=114b506c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d70c5eb3fa4b0935daa8b34778b2d1fd396a5ae5","tid":1630414,"uid":255323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0198162acc1d1e081c23c1724e6053b3ea86cc5e","tid":1630414,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49aa1c333f3cbc06e603b95c928592ca484949b2","tid":1630414,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cbd37ad228f2bfc104c20a6295fcb356a10ebdd","tid":1630414,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"努力玩緊"},{"pid":"62440fd1c28ee4be65b180b268993577a5e5e03f","tid":1630414,"uid":246369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"無人推？"},{"pid":"146c6ef6780b5e8a0f85502cb6279c2298bc85a8","tid":1630414,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e4a6f861270740f026cd8a2cc9642085da8d17","tid":1630414,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:40:07.000Z","msg":"會唔會令人聯想到侵再俾反侵人士吵?"},{"pid":"8e5114346cb2229e94be1984bc83fbb8afd9ea35","tid":1630414,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"你都白痴<br />\n應該係無論係咪假新聞/抹黑<br />\n只要對我地不利既一律要講fake news/共產黨宣傳"}]}